## SAFETY-PHRASE CALIBRATION CHECK

Before starting a chronicle, run through:

- ☐ Have I told the AI which safety phrases I'll use?
- ☐ Have I explained any phrases I want to modify or add?
- ☐ Have I confirmed the AI will honor them without justification request?
- ☐ Do I have the quick-reference card available during play?

If any answer is no, address it before continuing.
